Usage: cure <option>

<option> can be 'wounds' and 'poison'. You can cure serious wounds for some SP.
Or you can cure your poisoness.

You can now specify the wounds you want to heal.
  light, serious, critical wounds.
The more you heal the more it costs.
If you just type 'cure wounds' all your spellpoints, but 20 are taken to heal 
you.

